title: Jeffris, Wisconsin
text:
Jeffris is an <a href="Unincorporated%20area">unincorporated community</a> located in the town of <a href="Harrison%2C%20Lincoln%20County%2C%20Wisconsin">Harrison</a>, <a href="Lincoln%20County%2C%20Wisconsin">Lincoln County, Wisconsin</a>, United States.
History.
A post office called Jeffris was established in 1891, and remained in operation until it was discontinued in 1930. The community was named for James K. Jeffris.
